mySystemMIB.name: mySystemMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

mySystemMIB.description: This module defines my system mibs.

mySystemHwVersion.name: mySystemHwVersion
mySystemHwVersion.description: Return the string of the Revision number of hardware resides on the FastSwitch.

mySystemSwVersion.name: mySystemSwVersion
mySystemSwVersion.description: Return the string of the Revision number of software resides on the FastSwitch.

mySystemSysCtrlVersion.name: mySystemSysCtrlVersion

mySystemParametersSave.name: mySystemParametersSave
mySystemParametersSave.description: Save all parameters changed in configuration by setting this object to any value but 0, set its value to 0 will cause no action of agent, otherwise all changes of prarameters will be saved for retrive when system is reset, if parameter is changed but not saved all changes will come to their original value when system down and up again, when query always return value 0.

mySystemOutBandRate.name: mySystemOutBandRate
mySystemOutBandRate.description: Determine the console(OutBand) baud rate : 9600 - 1,19200 - 2, 38300 - 3, 57600 - 4, 115200 - 5, when the console baud rate is other value will return value 0.

mySystemReset.name: mySystemReset
mySystemReset.description: This Object allow perform soft reset of system by setting its value to none zero. if a soft resetis performed, after this having completed a warm start trap will send to declare the state and when queried will always return 0.

mySwitchLayer.name: mySwitchLayer
mySwitchLayer.description: Which layer's device the switch in system

mySystemOutBandTimeout.description: The timeout of console.0 indicate that timeout function is disabled.

mySystemTelnetTimeout.name: mySystemTelnetTimeout
